  <name>Comic Chat: Reinked</name>
  <summary>Turn IRC conversations into live comic panels</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Comic Chat: Reinked is a native modernization of Microsoft Comic Chat.
      It connects to IRC networks and lays conversations out as comic panels
      with expressive characters and speech balloons.
    </p>
    <p>
      Reinked is a community project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by
      Microsoft.
    </p>
  </description>
